title: Died Suddenly - Documentary About the Devastating Effects of the Vaccine Bioweapon
cleaned_text:
As many of you already know, I am not a fan of Stew Peters at all, and he is one of the producers of this documentary. The fact that I am sharing it means that despite some of the questionable characters involved, there is something worthwhile here. This documentary could be a good way to get through to some friends and family who are still wondering why people they know and love have “died suddenly” the past few years. It’s absolutely heartbreaking and infuriating what has been done to the people of this world.
